        <item>
            <title>【實試】AI 中文校對能力大比拼，測試 ChatGPT、Copilot、Gemini、Wordvice AI、和 Claude 3.5 辨別錯別字、簡體字等能力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/11/ai-chinese-proofreading-test/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-chinese-proofreading-test</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/11/ai-chinese-proofreading-test/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 13:00:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Claude 3.5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Copilot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
